Name: dress-graph
Version: 0.3.1
Date: 2026-03-03
Author: Eduar Castrillo Velilla
Maintainer: Eduar Castrillo Velilla
Title: DRESS: A Continuous Framework for Structural Graph Refinement
Description: DRESS computes
 continuous edge similarity values on graphs. The base algorithm is provably
 at least as powerful as 2-WL in expressiveness, and each higher-order level
 adds one WL dimension. Computation cost is O(I * m * d_max) per run.
Categories: Graph Theory
Depends: octave (>= 5.0.0)
License: MIT
Url: https://github.com/velicast/dress-graph
